    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was just looking at some photos of the deep field from the james webb telescope... it's just too much. looking at all that empty space and realizing that every single thing i've ever felt, every person i've loved, every struggle i've gone through... it's just literally zero. it doesn't even register in the scale of things. it feels like i'm just wasting energy existing for no reason.",
